Draft Release Checklist

1) Update the gallery3 VERSION constant in modules/gallery/helpers/gallery.php

2) Tag the release, eg:
   $ git tag 3.0-beta-2
   $ git push --tags

3) Build the release, eg:
   php build.php 3.0-beta-2

4) Publish the release to sf.net
   rsync -avP -e ssh dist/gallery-3.0-beta-2.zip bharat@frs.sourceforge.net:uploads/

5) <insert docs about updating SF.net FRS stuff here>

6) Click "publish" on the GMC story

7) Update sf.net, freshmeat.net stories



